{"word":"οὐλαμός","slug":"οὐλαμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>οὐλαμός</b></el> <el>(οὐλᾰμός, οῦ, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εἴλω'><el>εἴλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a throng of warriors</i>, <el>οὐλαμὸς ἀνδρῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>later, <i>a troop</i> of cavalry, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>turma, ala</el>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}